---
---

<section id="about" class="py-24 md:py-32">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 md:px-8">
    <h2 class="text-center font-bold tracking-tight text-white" style="font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 44px);">
      Founders.
    </h2>
    <div class="mt-12 mx-auto max-w-3xl grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <!-- Tre -->
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/50 p-8">
        <img src="/founders/tre.jpg" alt="Tre Mansdoerfer headshot" width="64" height="64" loading="lazy" class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full object-cover mb-6 border border-slate-700" />
        <div class="flex items-center">
          <h3 class="text-[22px] font-bold text-white">Tre Mansdoerfer</h3>
          <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/tremansdoerfer/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" aria-label="Tre Mansdoerfer on LinkedIn">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="ml-2 inline-block text-slate-500 hover:text-white transition-colors">
              <path d="M19 0h-14c-2.761 0-5 2.239-5 5v14c0 2.761 2.239 5 5 5h14c2.762 0 5-2.239 5-5v-14c0-2.761-2.238-5-5-5zm-11 19h-3v-11h3v11zm-1.5-12.268c-.966 0-1.75-.79-1.75-1.764s.784-1.764 1.75-1.764 1.75.79 1.75 1.764-.783 1.764-1.75 1.764zm13.5 12.268h-3v-5.604c0-3.368-4-3.113-4 0v5.604h-3v-11h3v1.765c1.396-2.586 7-2.777 7 2.476v6.759z"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-1 text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-foggy-teal">CEO</p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-foggy-text">
          Tre spent four years on Microsoft Azure's edge compute and CDN team, working on infrastructure for markets where full hyperscale campuses didn't pencil out. The economics he watched there are what eventually convinced him to start Foggy: the cloud is structurally not coming to most of the world.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Nicolas -->
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/50 p-8">
        <img src="/founders/nicolas.jpg" alt="Nicolas Weninger headshot" width="64" height="64" loading="lazy" class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full object-cover mb-6 border border-slate-700" />
        <div class="flex items-center">
          <h3 class="text-[22px] font-bold text-white">Nicolas Weninger</h3>
          <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/weninger/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" aria-label="Nicolas Weninger on LinkedIn">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="ml-2 inline-block text-slate-500 hover:text-white transition-colors">
              <path d="M19 0h-14c-2.761 0-5 2.239-5 5v14c0 2.761 2.239 5 5 5h14c2.762 0 5-2.239 5-5v-14c0-2.761-2.238-5-5-5zm-11 19h-3v-11h3v11zm-1.5-12.268c-.966 0-1.75-.79-1.75-1.764s.784-1.764 1.75-1.764 1.75.79 1.75 1.764-.783 1.764-1.75 1.764zm13.5 12.268h-3v-5.604c0-3.368-4-3.113-4 0v5.604h-3v-11h3v1.765c1.396-2.586 7-2.777 7 2.476v6.759z"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-1 text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-foggy-teal">CTO</p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-foggy-text">
          Nicolas spent four years as an embedded software engineer at Zipline, helping ship Platform 2 — autonomous drone delivery operating across Rwanda, Ghana, Kenya, and Nigeria. He spent last summer on AWS's EC2 capacity planning team, working with the largest customers on hyperscaler compute supply. He leads engineering at Foggy.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
